      <title>根據《華爾街日報》報道，Skydance 預計未來幾年營收將增加一倍以上</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/skydance-expects-more-than-double-its-revenue-coming-years-wsj-reports-2024-04-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據《華爾街日報》週五報道，Skydance Media 正在與派拉蒙全球公司進行獨家合併談判，預計未來幾年收入將增加一倍以上，調整後收益將增加兩倍以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/skydance-expects-more-than-double-its-revenue-coming-years-wsj-reports-2024-04-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 23:10:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
